These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, writing, photography, sudoku, gardening, card-games
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia, ebony, coral, light-blue, blood-red, apricot
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person who likes coral and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who likes orange is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | filmmaking     | gardening | board-games | photography | card-games  | writing  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Color         | fuchsia   | apricot | coral    | ebony  | light-blue | blood-red | orange |

