 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is the thai##1
 6. the british is the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the british is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who likes ivory##2
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the indian is on the right of the british##1
12. the person who likes ebony is the canadian##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
14. the egyptian is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
15. the canadian is on the far right##1
16. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the thai##1

