 5. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking water##1
15. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

