10. the dressmaker is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the fisherman##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is the nurse##1
13. the project-manager is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

