 9. the victorian house is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person eating cauliflower is the ranch-style house##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is the ranch-style house##1
13. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
