16. the person drinking soy-milk is between the havana-smoker and the person traveling to san-francisco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | tea      | mirinda | water     | coffee     | soy-milk   | milk |
| Cigar       | vegafina    | siglo | old-henry    | montecristo | alhambra     | ritmeester | havana |
| City        | edinburgh    | miami | new-york    | prague    | san-francisco | hannover | london |

